titles.title: Wagamama Oujo ni Tsukaeta Bannou Shitsuji, Tonari no Teikoku de Saikyou no Gunjin ni Nariagari Musou suru
The Versatile Butler Who Served a Selfish Princess Will Become a Peerless Upstart Soldier in the Neighbouring Empire
わがまま王女に仕えた万能執事、隣の帝国で最強の軍人に成り上がり無双する
Fed Up with Being the Spoiled Queen's Genius Butler, I Ran Away and Built the World's Strongest Army

title: Wagamama Oujo ni Tsukaeta Bannou Shitsuji, Tonari no Teikoku de Saikyou no Gunjin ni Nariagari Musou suru
title_english: Fed Up with Being the Spoiled Queen's Genius Butler, I Ran Away and Built the World's Strongest Army
title_japanese: わがまま王女に仕えた万能執事、隣の帝国で最強の軍人に成り上がり無双する
title_synonyms: The Versatile Butler Who Served a Selfish Princess Will Become a Peerless Upstart Soldier in the Neighbouring Empire
synopsis:
Leet isn't just any butler. His mistress, Princess Kilik, demands the impossible—and he delivers it, seven times before breakfast. But one day, Leet decides enough is enough, and he flees for a neighboring land where the talented rise up through the ranks instead of languishing in thankless, dead-end jobs. Under a new name, Lilt, he enrolls in a training and job placement program, and rapidly discovers that, easy as "wax on, wax off," his butlering skills make him a valuable asset!

(Source: MU)
background: Wagamama Oujo ni Tsukaeta Bannou Shitsuji, Tonari no Teikoku de Saikyou no Gunjin ni Nariagari Musou suru has been published in English as Fed Up with Being the Spoiled Queen's Genius Butler, I Ran Away and Built the World's Strongest Army by Kodansha USA since April 30, 2024.
